Nice port. Hi-res menus, plenty of options, including gamepad support. No remapping, which is a shame. The game itself has framerate issues, but unavoidable, since this is an emulation of the original release, which struggled to run on its intended hardware. If you're a Metal Slug fan, and have an Android gamepad, don't be afraid to grab this release!
